12.01	Ford_Aerospace	Ford Aerospace	Ford Aerospace &amp; Communications Corp. was the aerospace and defense business of Ford Motor Company. It consisted of (at least) the Space Systems Division (later Space Systems/Loral) and the Western Development Labs (WDL) (later Loral WDL, and presently Lockheed Martin WDL).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/27/FordGlassHouse.jpg/150px-FordGlassHouse.jpg
